http://bristol.sourceforge.net

Installing
----------

You need:

automake
autoconf
m4
gtk+-dev 

To compile and install, run:

./autogen.sh
./configure
./make 
./make install

To remove the clutter from autotools, run:

./autoclean.sh

You can also import this folder as an Eclipse-CDT Project.

